The body of a woman has been found in waters near Herolds Bay on Saturday afternoon. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The body of a woman has been found in waters near Herolds Bay on Saturday afternoon. Police say a resident saw the body floating in the ocean and alerted authorities. READ: Body of two-year-old found near Herolds Bay This after a mother and her two children were reported missing in the area. eNCA correspondent Louise Karsten says police are still investigating.